          <h6 data-animate="fade-up">Strong positioning needs strong design.</h6>
          <p data-animate="fade-up">
            For blckwht.tv we created a visual identity that does not resolve opposites but makes them visible. Black and white form the design base, complemented by strong contrast, clear typography and a reduced formal language. Corporate design is not decorative here, it becomes a content-driven tool.
